<h1>
The Cookie Technology</h1></center>

<center><img SRC="tbullet.gif" height=19 width=24><b>cookie concept</b></center>

<ul>
<li>
<b>How cookies work:</b></li>
</ul>

<ul>
<ul>
<li>
<b><u>Server to Client</u></b></li>

<br><b>Cookies are small data structures delivered by a web server to a
web client.&nbsp; The web server may deliver one or more cookies to the
client.&nbsp; The client stores cookie data on its local hard drive.</b></ul>

<ul>
<li>
<b><u>Client to Server</u></b></li>

<br><b>In certain cases (determined by the data in the cookie itself),
the client returns the cookies to the server that originally delivered
it.</b></ul>
</ul>

